name: 60 Seconds (MichaelLykkeStrand, CWeed420, Wakashi)
description:
60 Seconds
60 seconds is a rhythm game where you play as a bunny on a quest for the golden carrot. Only the best bunnies reach the top, try to see if you can beat the odds and receive the golden carrot on each level.

Scores to reach:

ChipVibe - Difficulty 7/10
Bronze 3500
Silver 6000
Gold 7500

Vibe - Difficulty 3/10

Bronze 5500
Silver 6300
Gold 7100
